text: What if Humans painted Earth Yellow?
Then AumSum will also paint himself Yellow.
Firstly, if Humans painted Earth Yellow.
People who love red roses might leave for a different planet.
Secondly, if Humans painted Earth Yellow.
Other planets may start laughing at planet Earth.
Thirdly, if Humans painted Earth Yellow.
People who just bought gold may not  be able to easily find it anymore.
Fourthly, some people love to  keep their hair dark black.
If Humans painted Earth Yellow, these  people will be mightily disappointed.
Fifthly, if Humans painted Earth Yellow.
Traffic signals will stop working, traffic cops may not be able to control the situation.
Lastly, if Humans painted Earth Yellow.
Artist who just gave final touches to his painting will be extremely disappointed.
